g(\kappa) & =\Omega_{tE}\frac{e\iota}{mc}\frac{2}{v^{2}\varepsilon^{\prime}}-\left[2\frac{E(\kappa)}{K(\kappa)}-1\right].
\end{align*}

\end_inset

The function 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha_{n}$
\end_inset

 is
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
